<%- include('./layouts/header') %>

<div class="container mt-5">
  <div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-primary mb-4">
      Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) UI
    </h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted">
      A complete VRV-Assignment for implementing RBAC with Express.js, EJS,
      PassportJS, and MongoDB.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card shadow mt-4">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title text-success">Features</h4>
      <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>Express JS:</strong> Fast and minimalist web framework
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>EJS:</strong> Templating engine for rendering dynamic views
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>Styling:</strong> Includes Bootstrap and custom CSS
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>PassportJS:</strong> Local authentication (email & password)
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>Roles:</strong> Admin, Moderator, and Client
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>Authorization:</strong> Role-based route protection
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>Mongoose:</strong> MongoDB ORM for database operations
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card shadow mt-4">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title text-danger">
        User Manual: Steps to Use the Project
      </h4>
      <ol class="list-group list-group-numbered">
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Install dependencies using <code>npm install</code>.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Create a <code>.env</code> file with the following:
          <pre><code>SESSION_SECRET=your_secret_key
MONGODB_URI=your_mongo_connection_string
DB_NAME=your_database_name</code></pre>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Start the server using <code>npm start</code>.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Open your browser and navigate to:
          <a href="http://localhost:8000" target="_blank"
            >http://localhost:8000</a
          >.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Authentication:
          <ul>
            <li>Visit <code>/auth/login</code> to log in.</li>
            <li>Visit <code>/auth/signup</code> to create a new account.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Access user features at <code>/user</code>.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Admin features are accessible at <code>/admin</code>.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Flash messages provide feedback for actions.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="text-center mt-4">
    <p class="text-muted">
      Developed with ❤️ using Express.js and MongoDB
      |shashank100rabh295@gmail.com |
      <a
        href="https://github.com/shashank100rabh/role-based-access"
        target="_blank"
        >GitHub Repo</a
      >
    </p>
  </footer>
</div>

